# MovieVerse Gateway API Requests

@base_url = http://localhost:8080

### Movies
GET {{base_url}}/movies?limit=10

###
GET {{base_url}}/movies/1

###
POST {{base_url}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Example Movie",
  "overview": "A demo payload for MovieVerse.",
  "genres": "Drama, Thriller",
  "rating": 7.8
}

### Reviews
GET {{base_url}}/reviews?movie_id=1

###
POST {{base_url}}/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "movie_id": 1,
  "rating": 4.5,
  "review_text": "Loved the cinematography."
}

### Metadata
GET {{base_url}}/genres?limit=20

###
GET {{base_url}}/people?limit=20

